{"tid":1860320,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2月4日以後的屯元天","createTime":"2020-02-03T14:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T14:59:46.000Z","uid":211994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac686e1a69dd07ae53db347fe81bad21535f6e7c","tid":1860320,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:53:19.000Z","msg":"一車車蝗蟲進化成飛曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為原本充滿二噁英嘅空氣增添一點支那肺炎嘅色彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n西鐵站輕鐵站巴士站的士站成為高危地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n超市藥房比佢地買走哂買貴哂啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來元朗就已經好多水貨客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屯門醫院博愛醫院天水圍醫院多咗好多確診個案<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你住嘅大廈 可能有懷疑確診嘅支那人逃走入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知匿埋喺邊一層嘅後樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n街邊地下會多咗好多人類嘅糞便<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好唔記得 支那肺炎病毒會透過排泄物傳染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢個情況各區都會出現<br />\n但依家集中哂喺屯元天<br />\n人口密度急速提高 患病率會增加<br />\n<br />\n封咗關？<br />\n我又真係唔覺得邊撚度封咗關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c56e319d1151cbf48649cbdde3dbefff90bbf6","tid":1860320,"uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:54:16.000Z","msg":"矛盾大對決：元朗鄉黑VS支那飛曱甴"},{"pid":"8d9ddf60dc67bdbaedc36f869fb994c45342de54","tid":1860320,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:54:55.000Z","msg":"屯元天既人大部分都係市區返工，又會傳返出去"},{"pid":"950cf2c999832c88f75f2dce81249a2a1a1d1399","tid":1860320,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />\t手足唔好有事"},{"pid":"0d3c1a7931f2281dbb67993e09e8caa1820b1a4a","tid":1860320,"uid":1544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"本身未封之前都大把大陸人經深圳灣過屯元天啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}